Particulars of distribution of spawning: Most spawning and holding took place in the upper reaches of section surveyed. Coho noted in trib. 2 near highway culvert. This system has never been thoroughly evaluated for enumeration purposes.
COMMENTS ON CONDITIONS AFFECTING THIS ST: This system was chosen by Stock Assessment for a weekly spawner assessment.
